Here’s a simple recipe for Beef Tacos: ### Beef Tacos #### Ingredients: - 1 lb (450g) ground beef - 1 small onion, finely chopped - 2 cloves garlic, minced - 1 packet taco seasoning mix (or homemade: 1 tbsp chili powder, 1 tsp cumin, 1 tsp paprika, 1/2 tsp oregano, 1/2 tsp salt, 1/4 tsp black pepper) - 1/2 cup water - 8 small taco shells or tortillas - 1 cup shredded lettuce - 1 cup diced tomatoes - 1 cup shredded cheese (cheddar or a Mexican blend) - 1/2 cup sour cream - 1/2 cup salsa - Optional: diced avocado, jalapeños, cilantro, lime wedges #### Instructions: 1. **Cook the Beef**: In a large skillet, cook the ground beef over medium-high heat until browned. Break it up with a spoon as it cooks. Drain any excess fat. 2. **Add Onion and Garlic**: Add the chopped onion and minced garlic to the skillet with the beef. Cook for another 2-3 minutes until the onion is soft. 3. **Season the Beef**: Add the taco seasoning mix and water to the skillet. Stir to combine, then simmer for about 5 minutes, or until the sauce has thickened. 4. **Prepare the Toppings**: While the beef is cooking, prepare your taco toppings: shred the lettuce, dice the tomatoes, and grate the cheese. 5. **Assemble the Tacos**: Warm the taco shells or tortillas according to the package instructions. Fill each shell with a scoop of the seasoned beef mixture. Top with lettuce, tomatoes, cheese, sour cream, salsa, and any other desired toppings. 6. **Serve**: Serve immediately with lime wedges on the side for squeezing over the tacos. "What looked like morning was the beginning of endless night" From The Exorcist (1973) Few days ago, I was thinking about what should I play on piano (app) and I remembered a music that I learnt to play about a year ago. It was "Tubular bells" which is also commonly known as The Exorcist theme by many people. Then I proceeded to youtube to listen it and it lead to me rewatch the movie's many scenes. I used to hate The Exorcist before cuz I thought it was boring and nothing happened in the movie but the a rewatch changed my view on it. I started to realise how great it is and also the little details and craft went into the movie which is amazing. Couple of days ago I couldn't stop thinking about the poster of the movie, It was so catchy and unique, like a guy standing under the street lamp, looking at the window knowing he is above to witness the greatest evil, A war is about to start between God and Devil. That's why I decided to paint it on paper. I usually uses either only pencil or crayons+sketch markers to draw my stuff because I don't/can't draw with paint brush properly, I'm not that good with painting but I decided to make it with paint for some unknown reason. So yeah here it is, I know it's not looking great but I put a lot of time and effort in it. Maybe I'll make more paintings from now on. Let me know your thoughts in the comments and also rate it out of 10.

Lantas, bagaimanakah cara melepas gigitan tokek dan benarkah gigitan tokek hanya akan lepas jika mendengar suara petir? Dilansir dari kompas.com Dosen Departemen Ilmu Penyakit Dalam Fakultas Kedokteran Hewan UGM Dr. drh. Slamet Raharjo, MP menjelaskan bahwa binatang seperti tokek ketika menggigit rahangnya akan mengunci. Hal itu yang membuatnya sulit dilepaskan ketika menggigit orang. “Pada dasarnya semua reptil dari sub ordo Sauria seperti biawak, kadal, iguana, tokek, dkk, ketika menggigit rahang akan mengunci sehingga agak sulit untuk dilepaskan,” ujar Slamet dihubungi Kompas.com, Jumat (21/10/2022). Slamet mengatakan, salah satu cara agar bisa terlepas dari gigitan tokek adalah meletakkan tokek pada benda kasar. Tujuannya agar tokek bisa menempel atau berpegangan. “Setelah kaki menempel biasanya tokek akan bergerak dan gigitan mengendur kemudian terlepas,” terangnya. I finally made roasted rabbit! Every time I have had rabbit when I was out to eat I have enjoyed it! Rabbit is a white meat with taste similar to a much more flavorful chicken. The meat is tender, juicy and so delicious! There’s not much fat in rabbit and it doesn’t have an outer like what you get with chicken so I decided to do an overnight brine. I went with a garlic and lemon heavy brine! These rabbits came already cleaned so luckily I didn’t have to do the gnarly stuff. Once the rabbits were brined I let some of that liquid dry off then I seasoned them with garlic butter seasoning! I kept it super simple and roasted the rabbits at 275F and brushed with garlic butter throughout the cook. I used my @thermopro TempSpike Plus to reach that perfect 160F internal temperature! The final result was absolutely delicious. I really love shredded meats and I can’t wait to use the juicy shredded rabbit in other recipes ❤️

The Mercedes-Benz CLR is a sports car developed by Mercedes-Benz in collaboration with AMG and HWA GmbH ¹. It was designed to meet Le Mans Grand Touring Prototype (LMGTP) regulations, and the CLRs were intended to compete in sports car events during 1999, most notably at the 24 Hours of Le Mans, which Mercedes had last won in 1989. It was the third iteration in Mercedes’ 1990s sports cars, succeeding the Mercedes-Benz CLK LM, which in turn was born of the CLK GTR. Similar to its predecessors, CLR retained elements of Mercedes-Benz’s production cars, including a V8 engine loosely based on the Mercedes M119 as well as a front fascia, headlamps, and grille inspired by the then-new Mercedes flagship CL Class. Three CLRs were entered for Le Mans in 1999 after the team performed nearly 22,000 miles of testing Disclaimer I didn't intend to infringe copyright and Didn't intend to profit from it I have Modified the work and added my own original material to it I found this content available on the Internet Saw that others posted the same content as well I Think that the use is a fair use.
